dct_title_s: A topographical map of Kittatinny Valley and Mountain in Sussex County and the northern part of Warren : from original surveys and levelings, based on the triangulation of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contour lines and spot heights. Contour interval 20 feet. At top margin: Geological Survey of New Jersey. Atlas sheet no. 1 (Kittatinny). "Surveys made in 1884, railroads revised to date." Historic Maps copy has ms. additions in red pencil.
dct_publisher_sm: [Trenton, N.J.] : Geological Survey of New Jersey, 1894 (N.Y. : Julius Bien & Co. Lith.)
